videos.headline: Tyree Appleby buries back-to-back 3s to extend Florida's lead
videos.description: Tyree Appleby is on fire as he drains back-to-back 3-pointers to give the Gators an early lead.

videos.headline: Colin Castleton drives and drains the and-1 for Florida
videos.description: Colin Castleton fakes out his defender and drives into the paint for the and-1.

videos.headline: Phlandrous Fleming with the absolute dime to Tyree Appleby for 3
videos.description: Tyree Appleby hauls in the dime from Phlandrous Fleming Jr. and drills the 3-pointer to give the Gators the lead.

videos.headline: Davonte Davis knocks down the 3 from deep for Arkansas
videos.description: Davonte Davis gathers the rock and drills the 3-pointer from deep to tie the game at 23-23.

videos.headline: JD Notae muscles through his defender and drains the shot for Arkansas
videos.description: JD Notae won't be denied as he knocks down the heavily contested layup to extend the Razorbacks' lead.

videos.headline: Brandon McKissic fires up the crowd with this massive and-1 for Florida
videos.description: The crowd goes wild as Brandon McKissic drains the and-1 to extend the Gators' lead in the second half.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Brandon Mckissic gets the and-1 to fall) 2022/02/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Colin Castleton says his defender is 'too small' as he drains the and-1
videos.description: Despite tight coverage, Colin Castleton somehow drains the and-1 for the Gators.

videos.headline: Davonte Davis takes it coast-to-coast for a clutch Arkansas bucket
videos.description: Davonte Davis gathers the rock and takes it coast-to-coast to extend the Razorbacks' lead late in the second half.

videos.headline: JD Notae crosses his defender and drills the clutch 3 for Arkansas
videos.description: JD Notae puts a nasty move on his defender and knocks down the 3-pointer to seal the victory over Florida on the road.
